<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>英语-VICE</title><link>https://www.vice.com/en/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 02:11:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>说唱歌手特维斯塔 (Twista) 欠税 44 万美元，可能入狱五年</title><link>https://www.vice.com/en/article/rapper-twista-could-serve-five-years-in-prison-after-accumulating-440000-in-tax-debt/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;芝加哥传奇说唱歌手 Twista 可能因未缴纳价值 44 万美元的税款而面临最高五年的监禁。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;说唱&lt;a href="https://www.vice.com/en/article/rapper-twista-could-serve-five-years-in-prison-after-accumulating-440000-in-tax-debt/"&gt;歌手特维斯塔 (Twista) 因欠下 44 万美元的税款可能会入狱五年，&lt;/a&gt;该帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.vice.com"&gt;VICE&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jun 2026 19:22:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.vice.com/en/article/rapper-twista-could-serve-five-years-in-prison-after-accumulating-440000-in-tax-debt/</guid></item><item><title>GTA 6 和 RDR2 截图对比显示 Rockstar 在图形方面取得了 8 年的惊人飞跃</title><link>https://www.vice.com/en/article/gta-6-and-rdr2-screenshot-comparison-shows-rockstars-stunning-8-year-leap-in-graphics/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;对 GTA 6 和 RDR2 的并排比较显示了 Rockstar 高级游戏引擎在过去几年中取得的进步。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.vice.com/en/article/gta-6-and-rdr2-screenshot-comparison-shows-rockstars-stunning-8-year-leap-in-graphics/"&gt;《GTA 6》和《RDR2》后的截图比较显示 Rockstar 在图形方面取得了惊人的 8 年飞跃，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.vice.com"&gt;VICE&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jun 2026 18:55:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.vice.com/en/article/gta-6-and-rdr2-screenshot-comparison-shows-rockstars-stunning-8-year-leap-in-graphics/</guid></item><item><title>纳斯曾经解释过为什么他最初不想在 2021 年赢得格莱美奖</title><link>https://www.vice.com/en/article/nas-once-explained-why-he-didnt-initially-want-to-win-a-grammy-back-in-2021/